HEADWORD: Bockelet
<hw>Bock"e*let</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A kind of long-winged hawk; -- called also
<altname>bockerel</altname>, and <altname>bockeret</altname>.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

